Web Motion for Beginners: An Overview

Web Motion for Beginners is a series of courses designed to introduce you
to the emerging field of motion graphics for the web. It kicks off with this
course, an overview of the planning and creation process. Author Tom Green
reminds you to pay attention to the world around you, and emphasizes the
importance of storyboarding, project planning, and tool selection
